    <div class="leftContent">
      <div class="leftContentTitle">Top Electric Cycling Routes in the U.S (1)</div>
      <div class="leftContentSubtitle">
        <div>JANUARY 18, 2022</div><div>Share:<a href="#" class="facebookBtn"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a><a href="" class="twitterBtn"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a><a href="" class="pinterestBtn"><i class="fa fa-pinterest"></i></a><a href="" class="envelopeBtn"><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i></a><a href="#" class="linkedinBtn"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="leftContentBriefContent">
        <p>There are many reasons people choose to ride an electric bike over a regular bike. An electric bike can help you get further, faster than just about any other type of pedal-powered vehicle. There are plenty of options when it comes to the best routes you can take on your electric bike. Here are some standout destinations for those who enjoy biking and want to take their trip up a notch.</p>
      </div>
